        and `\gamma, \delta \in \{ -1,+1 \}` such that the matrix

        .. MATH::

            N = \begin{bmatrix}
            \gamma & \delta & 0 \\
            C_{i,k} & C_{i,\ell} & \alpha \\
            C_{j,k} & C_{j,\ell} & \beta
            \end{bmatrix}

